00:43:44,430 --> 00:43:47,270
 The return of Emperor Ying Yuan is coming soon. 

402
00:43:47,270 --> 00:43:53,960
 He will uncover the secret about his bloodline and unveil the identity of the ambusher. 

403
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:56,750
 The mystery surrounding the Divine-Devil War will be uncovered. 

